{title: Step It Up And Go}
{artist: The Everly Brothers}
{composer: Written by Jimmy Howard}

[C]Nickel is a nickel dime is dime
Get you a girl you [C7]can have a good time
You gotta [F]step it up and go you gotta [C]step it up and go
Well you [G7]can't stand back you gotta [F]step it up and [C]go
[C]Two old maids sittin' in the sand
Each one wishin' that [C7]the other was a man
Repeat #2
