But she ain't too old for [C7]to shift her gears
Repeat #2
[C]Jumped in the river started to drown
Thought about my woman and [C7]I turned around
Repeat #2
[C]I knocked on the door about half past ten
She said listen here baby [C7]you can't come in
Repeat #2
